itemDescription: 5th Baron Harlech, Member of Parliament and Ambassador to the United States (1918-1985)

wikipedia_page.main: William David Ormsby-Gore, 5th Baron Harlech  (20 May 1918 – 26 January 1985), known as David Ormsby-Gore until June 1961 and as Sir David Ormsby-Gore from then until February 1964, was a British diplomat and Conservative politician.
